   strategy into true dynamic marketing policies that adjust pricing as
   customer relationships evolve. In this paper, we describe a dynamic
   programming-based approach to creating optimal relationship pricing
   policies. The methodology has two main components. The first component
   is a latent class logit model that is used to model customer buying
